Modifications by Louie Bao (2025):
- Adapted layout and UI for foxi-tools project
- Added fishing boat with procedural fisherman figure
- Added painter's algorithm depth sorting for boat/tree layering
- Added SVG download (SAVE button)
- Added red seal stamp decoration
- Added Easter egg: press B to highlight the boat in gold
- Fixed NaN rendering bug on ARM (mobile) devices
